{"word":"G2540 - καιρός - kairós - kahee-ros' - Always","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">καιρός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>kairós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>kahee-ros'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Always"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"காலம், சமயம், நாள், வேளை, இம்மை, வயது - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. due measure"},{"paragraph":"2. a measure of time"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> Of uncertain affinity; an <i>occasion</i>, that is, <i>set</i> or <i>proper</i> time: - X always, opportunity, (convenient, due) season, (due, short, while) time, a while. Compare <a href=\"#/G5550 - χρόνος - chrónos - khron'-os/5550\">G5550</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G170 - ἀκαιρέομαι - akairéomai - ak-ahee-reh'-om-ahee/170\">G170</a>, <a href=\"#/G171 - ἀκαίρως - akaírōs - ak-ah'-ee-roce/171\">G171</a>, <a href=\"#/G2120 - εὐκαιρία - eukairía - yoo-kahee-ree'-ah/2120\">G2120</a>, <a href=\"#/G2121 - εὔκαιρος - eúkairos - yoo'-kahee-ros/2121\">G2121</a>, <a href=\"#/G2122 - εὐκαίρως - eukaírōs - yoo-kah'-ee-roce/2122\">G2122</a>, <a href=\"#/G2540 - καιρός - kairós - kahee-ros'/2540\">G2540</a>, <a href=\"#/G4340 - πρόσκαιρος - próskairos - pros'-kahee-ros/4340\">G4340</a>"}]}